Happy birthday to my favorite brother!! On this day many years ago I was just an only child waiting to meet this little brother everyone was telling me I would love. I yelled “Come into the light!!” And then I finally got to meet him… and I instantly fell in love. I went from not being sure whether I wanted a brother to knowing I’d beat up anyone who hurt him. He is funny, smart, creative and so loving. I couldn’t be prouder of him… and I’d still beat someone up for him. He may be taller than me now, but he’ll always be my baby brother. Happy birthday bubba, love you to the moon and back❤️❤️🎉🎉🎉
#littlebrother #happybirthday #bigsister
